OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784445484
OL,3,CUS launches new Iran strikes after
OL,4,CJordan attack kills two US soldiers
OL,6,FThe US military has said it carried
OL,7,Fout new airstrikes against Iran to
OL,8,F"swiftly punish" the country's
OL,9,FRevolutionary Guard for an attack in
OL,10,FJordan that killed two American
OL,11,Fsoldiers.
OL,13,FThe strikes were designed to further
OL,14,Fdegrade Iran's ability to restrict the
OL,15,Ftraffic of oil tankers through the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz, US Central Command
OL,17,Fsaid, and marked an eighth consecutive
OL,18,Fnight of attacks on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
