OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784445484
OL,3,CUS launches new Iran strikes after
OL,4,CJordan attack kills two US soldiers
OL,6,FIn the Jordan attack another soldier
OL,7,Fwas left missing and four required
OL,8,Fhospitalisation.
OL,10,FThe new strikes came after the US
OL,11,Fmilitary announced its first troop
OL,12,Fdeaths from direct Iranian fire since
OL,13,Fthe opening days of the war, following
OL,14,Fa drone and missile attack on a base
OL,15,Fin Jordan on Friday. The dead were not
OL,16,Fidentified, and Central Command did
OL,17,Fnot offer any further details on the
OL,18,Fdeaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
