OL,3,CUS launches new Iran strikes after
OL,4,CJordan attack kills two US soldiers
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSince the war began, 16 US service
OL,12,Fmembers have been killed and over 430
OL,13,Fwounded.
OL,15,FAt least 3,636 Iranians, including
OL,16,F1,701 civilians, have been killed
OL,17,Fsince US and Israeli strikes began on
OL,18,FFebruary 28, according to Human Rights
OL,19,FActivists in Iran (HRA) reporting in
OL,20,FMay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
