OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784445484
OL,3,CUS launches new Iran strikes after
OL,4,CJordan attack kills two US soldiers
OL,6,FHRA verified the deaths of 307
OL,7,Fchildren and injuries to 2,213
OL,8,Fchildren as a result of the attacks.
OL,10,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,11,Fthreatened to target Iran's power
OL,12,Fstations and bridges to try to compel
OL,13,FTehran to loosen its hold on the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,16,FThe US in the past week also reimposed
OL,17,Fa naval blockade on Iranian ports to
OL,18,Fhalt its shipments of crude oil, and
OL,19,Fthe military said on Saturday it had
OL,20,Fredirected five ships and disabled one
OL,21,Fsince then.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
